::Prowl::

Prowl nods, feeling Iron Raptor's emotions. He looked back behind 
himself at all the other bots. They had survived once more. But yet, 
they were all very damaged, and would need to repair the CF soon.

He walks along with Iron Raptor, his arm around her waist and 
stroking ever so slightly, Prowl almost unaware of it. His thoughts 
fluttered back to the time they had spent in her quarters back at the 
Ark...

Prowl shakes out of those thoughts, looking at Iron Raptor and 
smiling. -Well, at least most of us are alive. Do you want to hear 
mine and Epyon's plan later?-
